  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your dealings with pirates, thieves, and assassins have taught you to be exceedingly careful.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Alertness, Combat Reflexes.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Opponents do not gain a +2 bonus on attack rolls for flanking you, although they can still sneak attack you. You also gain a +3 bonus on Sense Motive checks made to resist a foe's Bluff checks to feint in combat.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When an opponent attempts a feint against you, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the DC of the skill check made to feint by 1 per point of stamina spent.",
